69
00:03:25,410 --> 00:03:27,420
each with their own product idea

70
00:03:27,420 --> 00:03:30,006
that they will be pitching
to the team at large.

71
00:03:30,006 --> 00:03:31,590
(upbeat music continues)

72
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:35,640
They've poured a lot of
energy, thought and care

73
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,470
into these products,

74
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:41,163
so they're highly, highly
invested in each of their ideas.

75
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:45,270
But now they need to come
together to look at the facts

76
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:48,450
and set aside assertions to
choose the final product idea

77
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:49,950
that they'll all rally behind

78
00:03:49,950 --> 00:03:51,570
for the final prototype launch.

79
