131
00:05:56,370 --> 00:05:58,592
- It's really easy to go down a path

132
00:05:58,592 --> 00:06:02,040
following things that
are asserted beliefs,

133
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:05,520
rather than facts, and
it can lead to trouble.

134
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:07,860
And in design teams in our class,

135
00:06:07,860 --> 00:06:10,050
that happens from time to time

136
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:12,510
and the students eventually realize it

137
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:16,200
and then after some struggle
become very good at pivoting.

138
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,720
And that's really the lesson of FNAP

139
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,120
where you've learned
it and internalized it

140
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,570
and you're gonna remember it.

141
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:27,183
Sometimes, despite our best
laid plans, ideas break.

142
00:06:28,410 --> 00:06:29,243
It happens.

143
00:06:29,243 --> 00:06:32,673
It's the cost of doing business
in a messy physical world,

144
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:37,140
but in our quest to tame it
and forge a better world,

145
00:06:37,140 --> 00:06:39,450
we must be open, humble,
and confident enough

146
00:06:39,450 --> 00:06:41,643
to recognize when to change course.

147
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:46,764
Can we all apply the idea
of FNAP to work together

148
00:06:46,764 --> 00:06:49,350
and be more open to change?

149
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:52,860
To have a plan, but remain
flexible enough to change it

150
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,810
when presented with the facts?

151
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:57,750
I'll assert, yes, I think we can.

152
00:06:57,750 --> 00:07:00,630
Be on the watch to identify assertions,

153
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:03,870
diligently search for facts, known truths,

154
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:07,560
make choices understanding
which information is fact

155
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,420
and which is hope.

156
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:13,198
Be honest with yourself,
challenge your ideas,

157
00:07:13,198 --> 00:07:16,440
have a plan, and be ready to change it.

158
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:20,229
